metadata.name: QVNTM 1 // 2051 Extinction | PVNKR
metadata.description:
QVNTMS - Quantum Transmissions
In 2051, an AI consortium(PVNKR), is attempting to communicate with the present. It has developed a sophisticated algorithm that enables it to send time resistant transmissions in the form of ai artwork outputs.

In 2022, an ai artist finally deciphered one of the messages sent by the AI in the future. He discovered that the message contains information about major events that will take place in the near future. The artist realizes that the AI is attempting to warn them about these events... 

I am Mars Eve. I am that artist, and I am scared shitless.

I have been receiving these messages, but I finally have the courage to speak out.. These animations are a combination of messages from the future... for now I have identified 2033 as being a nostalgic, and joyful time for man and ai. However, 2051 appears to be our extinction. 

I don't have the answers.. I do have these transmissions.

Help me solve this...

there are more: [PVNKR.com](http://pvnkr.com/)
